#. <section class="sutta" id="an5.41"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an5.41:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 5"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 5"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.41:0.2"
msgid "5. Muṇḍarājavagga"
msgstr "5. With King Muṇḍa"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: pañcabhogaādiyasuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an5.41:0.3"
msgid "41. Ādiyasutta"
msgstr "41. Getting Rich"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli3.45"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an5.41:1.1"
msgid ""
"Ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme."
msgstr ""
"At one time the Buddha was staying near Sāvatthī in Jeta’s Grove, "
"Anāthapiṇḍika’s monastery."

msgctxt "an5.41:1.2"
msgid ""
"Atha kho anāthapiṇḍiko gahapati yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā "
"bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinnaṃ kho "
"anāthapiṇḍikaṃ gahapatiṃ bhagavā etadavoca:"
msgstr ""
"Then the householder Anāthapiṇḍika went up to the Buddha, bowed, and sat "
"down to one side. The Buddha said to him:"

# BB’s “utilization” echoes DPPN’s “use”, but comm says bhogānaṃ ādātabbakāraṇāni. It seems a big stretch to “utilization”. Thanissaro has “benefits that can be obtained from wealth”. But I follow Hare.
msgctxt "an5.41:1.3"
msgid "“pañcime, gahapati, bhogānaṃ ādiyā."
msgstr "“Householder, there are these five reasons to get rich."

msgctxt "an5.41:1.4"
msgid "Katame pañca?"
msgstr "What five?"

msgctxt "an5.41:1.5"
msgid ""
"Idha, gahapati, ariyasāvako uṭṭhānavīriyādhigatehi bhogehi "
"bāhābalaparicitehi sedāvakkhittehi dhammikehi dhammaladdhehi attānaṃ sukheti "
"pīṇeti sammā sukhaṃ pariharati;"
msgstr ""
"Firstly, with his legitimate wealth—earned by his efforts and initiative, "
"built up with his own hands, gathered by the sweat of the brow—he makes "
"himself happy and pleased, keeping himself properly happy."

msgctxt "an5.41:1.6"
msgid "mātāpitaro sukheti pīṇeti sammā sukhaṃ pariharati;"
msgstr "He makes his mother and father happy …"

msgctxt "an5.41:1.7"
msgid "puttadāradāsakammakaraporise sukheti pīṇeti sammā sukhaṃ pariharati."
msgstr ""
"He makes his children, partners, bondservants, workers, and staff happy …"

msgctxt "an5.41:1.8"
msgid "Ayaṃ paṭhamo bhogānaṃ ādiyo."
msgstr "This is the first reason to get rich."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an5.41:2.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, gahapati, ariyasāvako uṭṭhānavīriyādhigatehi bhogehi "
"bāhābalaparicitehi sedāvakkhittehi dhammikehi dhammaladdhehi mittāmacce "
"sukheti pīṇeti sammā sukhaṃ pariharati."
msgstr ""
"Furthermore, with his legitimate wealth he makes his friends and colleagues "
"happy …"

msgctxt "an5.41:2.2"
msgid "Ayaṃ dutiyo bhogānaṃ ādiyo."
msgstr "This is the second reason to get rich."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an5.41:3.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, gahapati, ariyasāvako uṭṭhānavīriyādhigatehi bhogehi "
"bāhābalaparicitehi sedāvakkhittehi dhammikehi dhammaladdhehi yā tā honti "
"āpadā—"
msgstr ""
"Furthermore, with his legitimate wealth he protects himself against losses "
"from such things as fire, water, kings, bandits, or unloved heirs."

#. VAR: appiyato vā dāyādato → appiyato vā dāyādato vā (s1-3)
msgctxt "an5.41:3.2"
msgid "aggito vā udakato vā rājato vā corato vā appiyato vā dāyādato—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an5.41:3.3"
msgid ""
"tathārūpāsu āpadāsu bhogehi pariyodhāya vattati, sotthiṃ attānaṃ karoti."
msgstr "He keeps himself safe."

msgctxt "an5.41:3.4"
msgid "Ayaṃ tatiyo bhogānaṃ ādiyo."
msgstr "This is the third reason to get rich."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an5.41:4.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, gahapati, ariyasāvako uṭṭhānavīriyādhigatehi bhogehi "
"bāhābalaparicitehi sedāvakkhittehi dhammikehi dhammaladdhehi pañcabaliṃ "
"kattā hoti."
msgstr "Furthermore, with his legitimate wealth he makes five spirit-offerings:"

msgctxt "an5.41:4.2"
msgid "Ñātibaliṃ, atithibaliṃ, pubbapetabaliṃ, rājabaliṃ, devatābaliṃ—"
msgstr "to relatives, guests, ancestors, king, and deities."

msgctxt "an5.41:4.3"
msgid "ayaṃ catuttho bhogānaṃ ādiyo."
msgstr "This is the fourth reason to get rich."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli3.46"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "an5.41:5.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, gahapati, ariyasāvako uṭṭhānavīriyādhigatehi bhogehi "
"bāhābalaparicitehi sedāvakkhittehi dhammikehi dhammaladdhehi ye te "
"samaṇabrāhmaṇā madappamādā paṭiviratā khantisoracce niviṭṭhā ekamattānaṃ "
"damenti ekamattānaṃ samenti ekamattānaṃ parinibbāpenti, tathārūpesu "
"samaṇabrāhmaṇesu uddhaggikaṃ dakkhiṇaṃ patiṭṭhāpeti sovaggikaṃ sukhavipākaṃ "
"saggasaṃvattanikaṃ."
msgstr ""
"Furthermore, with his legitimate wealth he establishes an uplifting teacher’"
"s offering for ascetics and brahmins—those who avoid intoxication and "
"negligence, are settled in patience and gentleness, and who tame, calm, and "
"extinguish themselves—that’s conducive to heaven, ripens in happiness, and "
"leads to heaven."

msgctxt "an5.41:5.2"
msgid "Ayaṃ pañcamo bhogānaṃ ādiyo."
msgstr "This is the fifth reason to get rich."

msgctxt "an5.41:5.3"
msgid "Ime kho, gahapati, pañca bhogānaṃ ādiyā."
msgstr "These are the five reasons to get rich."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "an5.41:6.1"
msgid ""
"Tassa ce, gahapati, ariyasāvakassa ime pañca bhogānaṃ ādiye ādiyato bhogā "
"parikkhayaṃ gacchanti, tassa evaṃ hoti:"
msgstr ""
"Now if the riches a noble disciple gets for these five reasons run out, he "
"thinks:"

msgctxt "an5.41:6.2"
msgid ""
"‘ye vata bhogānaṃ ādiyā te cāhaṃ ādiyāmi bhogā ca me parikkhayaṃ "
"gacchantī’ti."
msgstr "‘So, the riches I have obtained for these reasons are running out.’"

msgctxt "an5.41:6.3"
msgid "Itissa hoti avippaṭisāro."
msgstr "And so he has no regrets."

msgctxt "an5.41:6.4"
msgid ""
"Tassa ce, gahapati, ariyasāvakassa ime pañca bhogānaṃ ādiye ādiyato bhogā "
"abhivaḍḍhanti, tassa evaṃ hoti:"
msgstr ""
"But if the riches a noble disciple gets for these five reasons increase, he "
"thinks:"

msgctxt "an5.41:6.5"
msgid "‘ye vata bhogānaṃ ādiyā te cāhaṃ ādiyāmi bhogā ca me abhivaḍḍhantī’ti."
msgstr "‘So, the riches I have obtained for these reasons are increasing.’"

#. VAR: Itissa hoti → itissa hoti avippaṭisāro (s1-3)
msgctxt "an5.41:6.6"
msgid "Itissa hoti ubhayeneva avippaṭisāroti."
msgstr "And so he has no regrets in both cases."

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
#. VAR: bhatā bhaccā → gatā tacchā (mr)
msgctxt "an5.41:7.1"
msgid "Bhuttā bhogā bhatā bhaccā,"
msgstr "‘I’ve enjoyed my wealth, supporting those who depend on me;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an5.41:7.2"
msgid "vitiṇṇā āpadāsu me;"
msgstr "I’ve overcome losses;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an5.41:7.3"
msgid "Uddhaggā dakkhiṇā dinnā,"
msgstr "I’ve given uplifting offerings to teachers;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an5.41:7.4"
msgid "atho pañcabalīkatā;"
msgstr "and made the five spirit-offerings."

#. <br>
msgctxt "an5.41:7.5"
msgid "Upaṭṭhitā sīlavanto,"
msgstr "I have looked after the ethical and"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an5.41:7.6"
msgid "saññatā brahmacārayo."
msgstr "restrained spiritual practitioners."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc8"></a>
msgctxt "an5.41:8.1"
msgid "Yadatthaṃ bhogaṃ iccheyya,"
msgstr "I’ve achieved the purpose"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an5.41:8.2"
msgid "paṇḍito gharamāvasaṃ;"
msgstr "for which an astute lay person"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an5.41:8.3"
msgid "So me attho anuppatto,"
msgstr "wishes to gain wealth."

#. <br>
msgctxt "an5.41:8.4"
msgid "kataṃ ananutāpiyaṃ."
msgstr "I don’t regret what I’ve done.’"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc9"></a>
#. VAR: Etaṃ → evaṃ (mr)
msgctxt "an5.41:9.1"
msgid "Etaṃ anussaraṃ macco,"
msgstr "A mortal person who recollects this"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an5.41:9.2"
msgid "ariyadhamme ṭhito naro;"
msgstr "stands firm in the noble teaching."

#. <br>
msgctxt "an5.41:9.3"
msgid "Idheva naṃ pasaṃsanti,"
msgstr "They’re praised in this life by the astute,"

#. <br>
#. VAR: pecca sagge pamodatī”ti → pecca sagge ca modatīti (si, pts1)
msgctxt "an5.41:9.4"
msgid "pecca sagge pamodatī”ti."
msgstr "and they depart to rejoice in heaven.”"

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an5.41:9.5"
msgid "Paṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""
